{"tid":1801304,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"和你shop最高峰會係新年果個星期，而家只係頭盤","createTime":"2019-12-28T13:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T14:29:40.000Z","uid":12599,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"499d6b106d9d3d73fea473e056b1cb8862763f46","tid":1801304,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"和你shop目標係要攬炒紅藍經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n呢個經濟圈最旺場唔係聖誕節，因為中国無呢個假期<br />\n<br />\n相反，過年前後一般都好多中国客要辦年貨同放大假去旅行<br />\n<br />\n今日上水嘅行動係好成功，唔係怕記者catpure到狙擊水客嘅畫面，反而係要將呢d畫面大量流通去中国，達到阻嚇作用<br />\n<br />\n因為廣東珠三角地區，而家係幾個鐘就可以到香港，一但過年前有緩和就無辦法對新年檔期有最大衝擊<br />\n<br />\n做本地生意商店影響相對會細好多，因為佢地客群係香港人<br />\n<br />\n手足搞和你shop, 一定要忍手到過年前後先可以全面進攻，聖誕節檔期只係頭盤，黑警而家只會保護中国人，唔會保護香港人嘅港奸來，一定要盡力保存最大力量去作長期抗爭<br />\n<br />\n最後請為呢幾日和你shop被捕同受傷手足默禱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"f4009f15430b2084e68b0ff19ed1b830d8d7e392","tid":1801304,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"[12.29行動]香港人抗爭的日與夜 集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e79d1068e69ce264195ec3163aa70d5df74b44cb","tid":1801304,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你shop 升級：熱情香港 好客之道 又點少得你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\"